{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Noble Connections, Ignoble Intentions</h2><br>The king has summoned you! Recent reports indicate that there's a spy amongst the court magicians. You are the only noble qualified to join them without alerting suspicion so it's left to you to investigate.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/1.png?t=1724981171\" /><br><br>Your parents are upset that you, future head of your noble family, do not have a spouse. They demand descendants and, fortunately for them, you're about to meet some high status peers.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/2.png?t=1724981171\" /><br><br>Off you go to the join the Court Magicians to capture a spy and a spouse (or more than one)!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/3.png?t=1724981171\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The court has a spy, connect disparate conversations, and capture them for the king.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/4a.png?t=1724981171\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/4b.png?t=1724981171\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/4c.png?t=1724981171\" /><br>Pay attention to the details.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Court magicians, connect with them through conversation, and capture their hearts.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/5a.png?t=1724981171\" /><br>Talk to the Court Magicians.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/6b.png?t=1724981171\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/6c.png?t=1724981171\" /><br>Make connections...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/5d.png?t=1724981171\" /><br>Capture hearts.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/6d.png?t=1724981171\" /><br>Or get rejections.<br><br>Some people are harder to court than others as their personalities and circumstances will vary.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your Own Story</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/7a.png?t=1724981171\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/7b.png?t=1724981171\" /><br><strong>Every play through is unique with:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Different characters featuring their own appearance, personalities, and histories.<br></li><li>A variety of events move the plot forward.<br></li><li>Multiple endings from romantic to tragic.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/8.png?t=1724981171\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>One conversation mechanic that simultaneously supports romantic interactions and thrilling deductions!<br></li><li>Uniquely generated plotlines and a scoring system add replay value.<br></li><li>Play the way that you want:<br>      Be romantic and find your one-true-love.<br>      Focus only on the investigation if you don't care to flirt.<br>      Marry all of your suitors (maybe avoid bad actors).</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/9.png?t=1724981171\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Watch Credits","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamc